15:34:07.000Z","msg":"推比民陣睇"},{"pid":"8f8d0c242a050f4a73ecdbe482944a5180fa8ba2","tid":1227713,"uid":68453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"口號都唔想叫<br />\n<br />\n著返件寫住嗰八個字嘅雨褸嚟行會唔會仲好？"},{"pid":"68ed90200c12d2c40721bff24983688eadf4b656","tid":1227713,"uid":188907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"各位手足，唔好學金鐘PP個位烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地尊重佢 同時希望佢安息<br />\n<br />\n但我地係同伴，一齊抗爭下去，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個都不能少</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如情緒受困 一定要求助<br />\n呢d事好平常 唔駛驚<br />\n我地會一齊行 齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9uERMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9uERMC.png&h=5f21c210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議越演越烈，周日及周三的反修例示威均演變警民衝突。災後心理輔導協會設立「救心熱線」，為受事件影響、對社會死心的市民提供心理支援服務，熱線為51815501。"},{"pid":"caa2d4bdfc8d0b40252a0218afba22136712d6a7","tid":1227713,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港</span></span>"},{"pid":"98b9c694abe6da646a8d95768b19fb282db1ca8e","tid":1227713,"uid":205455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f638f2c9084d6d86de649f0bce575fba6e7c0a1","tid":1227713,"uid":47091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"全面撤回送中<br />\n我們不是暴動<br />\n釋放學生傷者<br />\n林鄭下台<br />\nHelp Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XHfqdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XHfqdK.png&h=328161ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"本身想揾番呢張圖講少少嘢<br />\n<br />\n希望聽日大家保持冷靜，我認為聽日需要沉默去逼林鄭個殺人凶手交代。<br />\n<br />\n如果聽日衝咗，我驚所有嘢會被分心。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位聽日冷靜。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聽日我地要冷靜地用大量和理非嘅憤怒<br />\n<br />\n求下各位聽日要冷靜！！<br />\n<br />\n另外請各位唔好再分化落去！我明白情緒影響好深，我而家都係<br />\n<br />\n但我想大家諗深一層我講嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢嗰陣變咗前列腺"},{"pid":"e5b1fcecaa7e4ea2d3b4332aad94f8b4ee1445f2","tid":1227713,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPTqNu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPTqNu7.jpg&h=66089d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850ab7cbba4b601f25301fb94c911ac1edde3139","tid":1227713,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:41:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BCYi8SghK3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBCYi8SghK3g&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=cfdaa688\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BCYi8SghK3g</a>"},{"pid":"4bf08a98fefb71fdcfa4d37d442a9cc78c284176","tid":1227713,"uid":260557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"固然林鄭係殺人兇手，佢係要下台<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過我希望大家既焦點放返係我地本身既訴求，要求撤回惡法，釋放同停止檢控政治犯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗呢位手足都唔想我地既焦點放左係佢身上<br />\n<br />\n我地對準焦點先不枉佢既犧牲<br />\n<br />\n最後冇人想見到有第二個犧牲，香港人同進同退"},{"pid":"259c04c4ddfee8a05708db7453bb19592f1fd962","tid":1227713,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d966faf48edd2854837ca99e8164413a4c0db01a","tid":1227713,"uid":259302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"烈士已經出現左，我都好憤怒，但大家一定要冷靜，聽日好多人一家大細出，好多人甚至係睇完9／6同12／6先開始轉軑，佢地係和理非，唔會衝，亦衝唔起，本來講左和理非遊行，我地衝會再次分化和理非同勇武，唔好忘記12／6嘅小成功係和理非同勇武合作嘅結果，一旦分化，和理非係緊急關頭無制止力，勇武無左群眾基礎比嘅合理性，大家一盤散沙，我地就玩完。呢個係長爭抗爭，聽日大家先和理非，紀念烈士，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">君子之仇，十年未晚！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集中目標！<br />\n1.撤回修例<br />\n2.收回示威是爆動的定性<br />\n3.釋放所有過去一週因示威被捕的人<br />\n4.追究警方使用過份武力，甚至暴力"},{"pid":"8293befb596ade77eaa5d2ea7e43ce139374e4d5","tid":1227713,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"096ed8b4a8694eea8de7ab92b253a80444cfdbb8","tid":1227713,"uid":178320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a1c7e1c5ef69661652d3dfe2a9ad2f0abfcee22","tid":1227713,"uid":60434,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"黑警冷血 林鄭殺港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbcd4adc690ce0330c054cc9840c64ccce0560cb","tid":1227713,"uid":217761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"不撤不散，<br />\n賤婦下台"},{"pid":"79f9a8a293f78ebdc5063d31d9ab47d3766fe47c","tid":1227713,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"有冇牧師聽日遊行出發前領禱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1227770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1227770</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afbfb089af754c7354409e4066fe7f908e9d5e4d","tid":1227713,"uid":237747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06